<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='647000' id='t-647000'>That's why -- jump, like that? No, don't jump.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651000' id='t-651000'>Come back. Because, after, there is another trap.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654000' id='t-654000'>If you look like that, you look to the past,</span>
