11:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='664000' id='t-664000'>That's why every morning, now, because you are a good mutant,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='669000' id='t-669000'>you will raise your angle of view.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='673000' id='t-673000'>Out, more of the horizontal. You are an intelligence.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677000' id='t-677000'>Never forget -- like that, like that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='680000' id='t-680000'>It's very, very, very important.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='683000' id='t-683000'>What, what else we can say about that? Why do that?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692000' id='t-692000'>It's because we -- if we look from far, we see our line of evolution.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703000' id='t-703000'>This line of evolution is clearly positive.</span>
