<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='712000' id='t-712000'>But if you take a lens, like that, this line is ack, ack, ack, ack, ack. Like that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719000' id='t-719000'>It's made of light and shadow.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='724000' id='t-724000'>We can say light is civilization, shadow is barbaria.</span>
