</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='743000' id='t-743000'>That means, we can imagine -- I don't say it was fantastic,</span>
