<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='763000' id='t-763000'>In this case, people like me are acceptable.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767000' id='t-767000'>We can say, &quot;It's luxurious time.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='770000' id='t-770000'>We have time to think, we have time to I don't know what,</span>
